EmbedAzzyHelpDesc:
Here you can find all commands and their respective descriptions.
If you want to know more about a command, add it using the optional parameter of this command.
EmbedAzzyHelpOptionDesc: Use these additional parameters to change the behaviour of the command:
EmbedAzzyStatsMoreStats: More stats are only available on linux systems.
EmbedUpdatesAvailableDesc: Update now to get the latest bug fixes, features and improvements!
EmbedUpdatesAvailableChangelogTooBig: The changelog is too big to display it in an Embed, you can view it [here](%URL%).

Please inform %USER%.
